            "abstract": [
                {
                    "value": "Alfred Amery served as a volunteer in the MacKenzie-Papineau Battalion of the International Brigades in the Spanish Civil War. The collection contains two autobiographical manuscripts that focus on Amery's service during the Spanish Civil War, his experiences in the Armed Forces during the 1920s and 1930s, and his introduction to Communist politics. Also included is poetry by Amery on both personal and political themes.",
                    "id": "aspace_79d8d640847e6b01f62a1674d69b9e7f"
